title: Asus GM501 Zephyrus M - Cheaper AND Better!
description: My review of the Asus Zephyrus M - GM501. The best gaming laptop from Asus for thin and light performance at a cheaper price. Zephyrus M -   A powerful laptop i7-8750H with a GTX 1070 on a 144 Hz 3ms screen. This laptop has incredibly strong performance in a thin and light package. It now has a greatly improved keyboard and touchpad from the previous generation.
